<span class="grey">Jones, et al.           Expires January 30, 2014               [Page 19]</span>
</pre><!--NewPage--><pre class='newpage'><a name="page-20" id="page-20" href="#page-20" class="invisible"> </a>
<span class="grey">Internet-Draft          JSON Web Signature (JWS)               July 2013</span>


   o  Header Parameter Name: "x5t"
